rows.label: qst103912_msg0001
rows.name:
I can't believe you got a ship, Rex.
Actually, I suppose I can.

rows.label: qst103912_msg0002
rows.name:
Well, I'll set up the shipping
route as promised!
Nice work, guys.

rows.label: qst103912_msg0004
rows.name:
Oh, by the way, if I send 90,000G
using the new route, how much would
Auntie Correl receive?

rows.label: qst103912_msg0005
rows.name:
The handling fee between Avaritia
and Ysheva Harbor is set at 5%,

rows.label: qst103912_msg0006
rows.name:
It's further than Gula Province,
you see. An escort is pretty much
essential, too, so it bumps up the price.

rows.label: qst103912_msg0007
rows.name:
So you're looking at 85,500G
once it gets to Ysheva Harbor.

rows.label: qst103912_msg0008
rows.name:
Iyasaki itself is right by Ysheva Harbor
so there shouldn't be any additional
fees after that.

rows.label: qst103912_msg0009
rows.name:
Wow, that's quite a difference to
before! This shipping route was
well worth it.

rows.label: qst103912_msg0010
rows.name:
Oh, and it'll be even easier for
Correl to send you her home
cooking, won't it?

rows.label: qst103912_msg0013
rows.name:
It's not even a day old!
It looks so good.

rows.label: qst103912_msg0014
rows.name:
Great!
...Oh, there was something
I wanted to ask.

rows.label: qst103912_msg0015
rows.name:
It would really help me out if you
could lend my guards a hand with
their duties. Reckon you can do that?
